data.description: Beautiful 3 Bedroom 2 Bath Home on Wooded, Oversized Lot.  Located in the Tranquil Willow Brook Estates. Enjoy the Peaceful Views From the Huge Deck off the Eat-In Kitchen. Sunken Family  Room has Fireplace and 2 Sliding Glass Doors Leading to Large Screened-In Patio. New Furnace and New Stove. Large Yard Features a Shed and Wooden Play set. Large Basement. update: Property Includes Solar panels with an active 20 year account with Com-ED meaning, buyer will get free electricity for 20 years. which is a money saver in itself! solar panels also come with a warranty for the roof! home comes AS- IS. Very Motivated Seller!
